    • Love a Japanese-themed tee?

      Get ready to make a splash with this one-of-a-kind tee that blends traditional Japanese culture and modern fashion. The back features a striking bold print that blends iconic Kanji characters, and powerful waves in a truly eye-catching way with a small print on the front.

      Love Japanese culture or have an eye for art? This minimalistic tee is a must-have for your wardrobe. Make a statement and stand out from the crowd!

      Available in 12 colors and 6 different sizes, measurements are shown below.       We always recommend choosing 1-2 sizes larger and comparing the measurements in the sizing chart to a tee that fits you.

      Size (inches) S M L XL XXL XXXL
      Bust 36 38 41 43 45 47
      Length 26 27 28 29 30 31
                   
      Size (cm) S M L XL XXL XXXL
      Bust 92 98 104 110 115 120

      If you are interested in more items like this, please check out our website www.kawaiies.com



      Features

      🌊 100% Cotton
      🌊 Short oversized sleeves
      🌊 Designs printed on the front and back


      Measurements may be off by 1-5cm for rounding up to a whole number.

    • Please follow the washing labels when cleaning the garment:

       Max temperature 30c, or cold water. Reverse garment to protect the print.

       Do not bleach

       Dry by the sun or hang it to dry. 

       Dry cleaning
